name: KILL THE BLOB
description:
Rogue scientists in a level-4 bioweapons lab accidentally spill ketchup into their petri dish while eating a hotdog, and a super plague is born. This virus intends to devour the whole earth as retribution for those scientists devouring a delicious meal that contained a distant relative of itself, Heinz Ketchup. 

Only YOU can stop this cataclysm by joining the ranks of the other white dot fighters as they combat the ever-growing blob. 

Each NFT purchase increases the alliance force that will shoot the blob until it hopefully blows up in spectacular fashion. Be (kinda) amazed as the battlefield evolves when other Hicetnunc'ers join the war, and see your spot in the opposing forces blast away at the ghastly heap of black sludge.
